com.lars_albrecht.foldergen.core.generator.helper

Class StructItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lars_albrecht.foldergen.core.generator.helper.StructItem

  • public class StructItem
extends java.lang.Object
    StructItem is a special item for the Struct. The StructItem contains a name (String), a struct (Struct), additional data (Object) and a structItem (StructItem). The StructItem (parentStructItem) is null or the parent item.
    Version:
    1.0.0.0
    Author:
    lalbrecht
